' Connections showing evaluation flow
L1 --> L2 : Business drives technical
L2 --> L3 : Agent uses tools
L3 --> L4 : Tools enable reasoning
L4 --> L5 : Reasoning enables collaboration
L5 --> L6 : Agents use RAG
L6 --> L7 : RAG safety critical
L7 --> L8 : Safety enables compliance
L8 --> L9 : Compliance requires HITL
L9 --> L10 : HITL impacts operations
L10 --> L11 : Operations drive cost
L11 --> L12 : Cost impacts reliability
L12 --> L13 : Reliability needs memory
L13 --> L14 : Memory can hallucinate
L14 --> L15 : Detection needs monitoring

